{"type": "article", "id": 35741, "title": "Topshop 终于来了内地，以及，推荐一个日本眼镜品牌 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-19T02:48:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 35943, "name": "加拿大鹅"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 20048, "name": "Nordstrom"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 110, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161219104635wYPaHkeVEUiOm8cD.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/nordstrom-drops-most-since-may-after-jpmorgan-cuts-rating\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国高档百货连锁 Nordstrom 股价大跌，达七个月以来最大降幅</b></a> | 上周四，Nordstrom 的股票下跌了 9.2%，至 50.2 美元每股，这是自 5 月 13 日以来的最大单日降幅。J.P 摩根的分析师 Matthew Boss 认为，Nordstorm 没有重振停滞不前的销售，尽管它的电子商务目前已经占到总销售额的 20%。Nordstrom 用于电商的投资成本过高，目前还没找到平衡。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/economy/article/2054569/prada-close-boutique-peninsula-hotel-hong-kongs-retail-slump\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奢侈品牌在香港的门店纷纷关闭或缩减面积，分析师认为，这是健康的调整</b></a> | 上周，Prada 宣布要在年底之前从香港半岛酒店的商场中撤离，在这之前，Ralph Lauren、Burberry 和 Paul Smith 等品牌也都关闭或缩减了香港门店。但独立物业咨询机构 Knight Frank 的分析师认为，这是健康的调整，因为在过去 20 年，奢侈品牌为了吸引大陆游客在香港的开店数量翻了 2 倍。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/e35a5850-c395-11e6-9bca-2b93a6856354\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Topshop 要在内地开店 </b></a>| 继英国高街品牌 Topshop 在香港开设了三家门店之后，Topshop 终于要来内地开店了。据称，Topshop 此次将与尚品网合作，共同管理这些店铺。目前，Topshop 在英国国内共有 300 家店铺，以及 140 家海外店铺。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/vetements-x-canada-goose-collaboration-available\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 与加拿大羽绒品牌 Canada Goose 合作</a>，推出联名款羽绒服。这系列的羽绒服延续了 Vetements 一贯的宽大廓形和长袖子，一共四个颜色，均以保暖性极佳的羽绒进行填充，定价从 2685 到 3070 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101747KMifXsRYjmuFgGpQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101747gSAFPh9XB3L6QZvs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101756BjsxqOCHhAGfzkcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101756L1zRyPIAMkY8Ec4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">想要看起来更像是“纽约客”一点，不妨试试《New York Magazine》与棒球帽品牌 New Era 合作，带来的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/new-york-magazine-x-new-era-snapbacks\" rel=\"nofollow\">限量版 Snapback 系列</a>。该系列帽款分别加入了羊毛和丹宁材质，包括灰色、黑色和深蓝色，目前已于《New York Magazine》杂志官网发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101804HGLFTK6V0IfqWNBR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101804aBgFDLuft3OHMXro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/17/louis-vuitton-fantasy-boxes-2016/#slide-6\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 推出了 Fantasy Boxes 系列</a>，你可以用它来装巧克力、鲜花，或者是首饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101815QHCh2olygXFrkzB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101815FKZLCnzrIX1bMhPW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101815ZKoUthzicN3ylEI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101815qlrJjBHTK0YZ9zEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219101816FAXjzxmPRDeM69Tt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612191018166svKGE0BbdeqJg7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为了庆祝 KITH 成立五周年，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/ronnie-fieg-x-timberland-6-boots\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ronnie Fieg 与 Timberland 合作推出了 6-inch 40″ 联名靴款系列</a>，该系列共有四款颜色，已于 KITH 门店和线上店铺发售，限量 300 双。这系列鞋款均选用了上乘的麂皮和皮革，搭载防水内衬，是不错的冬季户外装备。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103051wQXvfNh9KyDIl6HF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103059I2liBfpUC8oqX3HT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103100bAh64TeEcMRwtQP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103100PxBI7prfmFGCYWHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103100SPkWo8vaz5cO2Y9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612191031003XhRcHIsJ9uxLv4Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103100GSoCIwzlpP5M9TJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103106TQtax2KlFnXJzdrq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">创立于 1984 年的日本手工眼镜品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/boston-club-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boston Club</a>，它的 2016 秋冬系列还不错。该系列延续了品牌的美式复古风格，四款新品都配备了光学眼镜以及太阳镜的款式。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103122fpqDXswazvQyVU1t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.418000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103132t8wmQWisqBTC3jdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103132iL6ArsI0gWy1ohFb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103132SMbiQjTs7EoHPXax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103142WPAvSuVj3hgfZYEB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.538000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612191031419gfDdAhYQruvGwC1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103142biKraG4t9whPq6dV.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103143LandOsQPDMExYw4J.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103150fwSZBQX2l1hYaP8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219103150WhtGv0osyLXBDj6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://bostonclub-eyewear.com/lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">bostonclub</a></p>"}